outputs.output_descr: An integrated national vision developed to guide the UN/UNDP in its efforts to support peace and development in the country through consolidating the ongoing initiatives aimed at enhancing conflict prevention and peace building capacities of national partner (government and non-government stakeholders), as well as exploring new opportunities for engagement.
